text: Tino Thömel (born 6 June 1988) is a German former professional road cyclist, who currently works as a directeur sportif for UCI Continental team . Thömel had eight professional wins in his career, as well as several more at lower levels. Three of his wins came in the Szlakiem Grodòw Piastowskich cycling race in Poland, with one stage win each in 2011, 2012 and 2013.
